name: remix-competition-live-out-loud
title: Remix Competition: Live Out Loud
description:
Since it's premiere on Hardwell On Air, fans eagerly anticipated the release of "Live Out Loud." Masterfully blending Angelika Vee's phenomenal vocal with his signature driving Power House bassline, Styline created the perfect soundtrack for living life to the fullest. Now he is excited for producers in all genres to put their spin on the track and work with Angelika Vee’s beautiful vocal.

Styline would like for this to be a creativity contest. The more creative the better, and he is excited to see different genres and styles. There will be no discrimination by the size of the artist, and all submissions will be closely listened too. If there are more than three deserving winners, we will pick them all!

Prize 

- The top three remixes will receive an official release on Styline's Own Maskade Records
- Social media support from Styline  
- Styline will reach out personally to the winners in a mentoring role to see what they need help with most at this point in their career

description:
With Sem Thomasson's Top 10 hit "We Are" doing so good, and receiving lots of praise and support worldwide; its time we gave something back! 

Sem has been kind to agree to let you guys remix his track! 

We are looking for cool, quality tracks that are different from the original. 

Ideally not too much on the "EDM" front, hardstyle kicks are a no go. Be creative, be smart. 

The winning remix will be chosen by Sem himself, together with Jamie from Zerothree, and will get a release on the label. 

Deadline is 1st March 2015. 

Download and enjoy!

name: rudy-zensky-gladiator-remix-contest
title: Rudy Zensky - Gladiator [ Remix Contest ]
description:
Rules and regulations: 
- We accept as a remix only the following genres: electro house, trap and progressive house. If your remix is other genre, it will be deleted. 
- We accept as submission only remixes with a preview of at least 3 minutes or higher. 
- If your submission is an original mix, set or anything not related with our Remix Contest, it will be DELETED.
- Be sure to push your remix into TOP 20, because Rudy Zensky and us will chose the winning remixes only from the first 20. So take your friends and ask them to help you.
 
The two winning remixes will be released on Ensis Records in all major stores. Also they will be heard by more than 40k EDM fans from our social network and our partners. Also, they will be send to a DJ list as promo to more than 400 names. As a reminder, our releases were supported during time by names like Hardwell , Markus Schulz , David Vendetta , Judge Jules, Paul Oakenfold, Juicy M , Cash Cash , Victor Niglio , Outwork, Dankann and many more. 　
　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　 
　
Dates: 
Remixes Submission : Jun 15th - Jul 15th
Voting: Jul 15th - Aug 15th
Winners announcement: Aug 16th

name: scovendo-alive-in-the-fire-remix-competition-1
title: Scovendo - Alive In The Fire [Remix Competition]
description:
The remix competition for Scovendo - Alive In The Fire ft. Nathan Brumley is now open! 

Scovendo brings you "Alive In The Fire"! Jam out to the fresh melodies brought to you by young Dutch producer Niels van den Broek better know as Scovendo featuring the talented Nathan Brumley's vocals!

Anywhere from 1-6 winning remixes will be selected as winners to be released on a "Alive In The Fire (Remixes) EP". There are no restrictions regarding how to use the stems, amount of stems, or type of remix. All genres of music will be accepted in this remix competition. The release date of The Remix EP will be announced on our Facebook page within the time that the remix competition is open. If you have any additional questions, comments, or concerns please send an email to info@novalotusproductions.com with "Alive In The Fire Remix Competition" in the subject line. Thank you for participating and we look forward to hearing all of the submissions!

Full Stop Records is offering again the chance to be noticed and have your remix released on the label! 

DJs and producers from around the world are invited to remix the hit 'Headbanger' by Dario Synth and Gravity Kicks.
(Listen the original here: https://soundcloud.com/dariosynth/dario-synth-vs-gravity-kicks-headbanger-original-mix)

Please, think outside the box and surprise us! 
We're looking for well produced, creative and fresh remixes to release. 
All music genres are welcome! 

Download the stems here and get to work. 
Make sure to get your friends and fans to vote for your entry so it will trends on the chart!

Please note: being ranked first doesn't mean you're going to win for sure, but it increase your chance to be noticed. 

Submissions/Voting from December 5th to January 5th.

Winner announced in the following weeks. 

Good work!

title: 'WE ARE' Remix Contest
description:
Full Stop Records is offering again the chance to be noticed and have your remix released on the label! 

DJs and producers from around the world are invited to remix the hit 'We Are' by Dario Synth, Matt3w & Sideone and Chess.
Listen to the original track here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUeb7e5cD90

Please, think outside the box and surprise us! 
We're looking for a well produced, creative and fresh remix to release. 
All music genres are welcome! 

Download the stems here and start to work. 
Make sure to get your friends and fans to vote for your entry so it will trends on the chart!

Please note: being ranked first doesn't mean you're going to win for sure, but it will increase your chance to be noticed. 

Submissions/Voting from June 21th to July 21th 2015.

Stay tuned to our official pages to know the winner!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fullstoprecords

Good work!
